5 Relationship between trait score and curiosity ratings between Familiar and Novel rooms

Here performance difference refers to difference in item recollection and source memory between the novel and familiar rooms (novel - familiar).

5.1 See whether the curiosity ratings are significantly different between novel and familiar rooms

The average curiosity rating for the novel rooms is 4.78 (SD = \(\pm\) 1.9).

The average curiosity rating for the familiar rooms is 3.08 (SD = \(\pm\) 1.71).
